lead_paragraph: Denzel Valentine started slow and finished strong with 19 points, eight rebounds and six assists to help No. 6 Michigan State beat Penn State 88-57 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: No. 6 Michigan State Beats Penn State 88-57 After Slow Start
